data.description: Executive home close to town with great views of the Tusquittee Mountains.Enter into the great room with cathedral ceiling, stone fireplace, large custom windows to enjoy the view.Lots of space for entertain-ing.Master is located on the main with double door entry.En-suite gives a spa like feeling with large soaker tub,separate shower and double sinks.Main level has it all with breakfast area,dining,large living room,half bath,master,laundry and oversized two car garage.Ter-race level features two nicely sized bedrooms,fitness room,bath,rec room(with 2nd fireplace) and loads of storage closets.Add'l features security system,whole house generator, paved driveway, high speed internet, and low maintenance exterior.Add'l features chain linked fence,trex decking,and landscaping placed just right for privacy from your neighbors.This is a court ordered private sale subject to NC G.S. 1-339.33 thru 1-339.40.
